data.description: PLEASE NOTE, PHOTOS ARE STOCK PHOTOS AND FEATURES, COLORS ETC, MAY VARY FROM ACTUAL MODEL:  NEW SMART HOUSE SYSTEM AT FRONT & BACK PORCH/FAMILY ROOM. $7500.00 upgrade value. LIFE BUILT HOMES presents the HOMESTEAD plan with covered back patio on full 1 acre lot plus 3 car garage. This Craftsman style plan has 5 bedrooms OR 4 bedrooms & finished media/bonus room & 3 1/2 baths, a luxury master on the main w/ a large bath,separate glass shower and huge walk in closet. The open floor plan offers a bright kitchen with granite counter tops, island, family room w/fireplace & breakfast with additional formal dining as well & 1/2 bath off foyer. Contact listing agent for preferred lender information and incentives.
